{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"43":{"eng-name":"General Behavior (Kitab Al-Adab)","ara-name":"كتاب الأدب"}},"section_detail":{"43":{"hadithnumber_first":4773,"hadithnumber_last":5274,"arabicnumber_first":4773,"arabicnumber_last":5274}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":4838,"arabicnumber":4838,"text":"حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْعَلاَءِ، حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ بِشْرٍ، عَنْ مِسْعَرٍ، قَالَ سَمِعْتُ شَيْخًا، فِي الْمَسْجِدِ يَقُولُ سَمِعْتُ جَابِرَ بْنَ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ، يَقُولُ كَانَ فِي كَلاَمِ رَسُولِ اللَّهِ صلى الله عليه وسلم تَرْتِيلٌ أَوْ تَرْسِيلٌ ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih Lighairihi"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":43,"hadith":66},"chapter":{"id":21,"ara-name":"باب الْهَدْىِ فِي الْكَلاَمِ","eng-name":"Manner of speech","isFirstHadith":false}}]}